@startuml
autonumber
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "Utente" as User
box "Frontend" #LightBlue
    participant "Login Page" as UI
end box

box "Backend (NextAuth)" #LightYellow
    participant "/api/auth/..." as NextAuth
    participant "Prisma Adapter" as Adapter
end box

box "Provider Esterno" #Orange
    participant "Google / GitHub" as Provider
end box

box "Database" #LightGreen
    database "Postgres" as DB
end box

User -> UI: Clicca su "Accedi con GitHub"
activate UI
UI -> NextAuth: Richiesta Login (signIn('github'))
NextAuth -> Provider: Redirect verso Provider (OAuth Authorize)
activate Provider

note right of User: L'utente autorizza l'app\nsu GitHub/Google

Provider -> NextAuth: Callback con "Authorization Code"
deactivate Provider

activate NextAuth

NextAuth -> Provider: Scambia Code con Access Token + User Profile
activate Provider
Provider --> NextAuth: Restituisce { email, name, image, id }
deactivate Provider

group Logica Nuovo Utente
    NextAuth -> DB: Check se utente esiste (by email)
    activate DB

    DB --> NextAuth: Nessun utente trovato
    NextAuth -> DB: createUser(profile)

    DB --> NextAuth: Oggetto User completo
    deactivate DB
end

NextAuth -> NextAuth: Crea Sessione (JWT/Cookie)
NextAuth --> UI: Success (Redirect URL)
deactivate NextAuth

UI -> User: Redirect to /verify
deactivate UI

@enduml